                    <h1>Gerona Kingdom Chapters</h1>
					<p>Gerona Kingdom is a country with massive territory that spans across a large portion of the earth and in which that many cultures formed, people living their lives and strange mysteries in the shadows for the citizens to discover and solve!</p>

					<p>Many characters inhabit the wonderous and magical land of Gerona, each with their own story to tell. Each book is it's stand-alone story so you can pick a character that appeals to you the most and jump in there. If you would like to see the characters of Gerona, click here!</p>

					<p>If you would like to help support the series, purchase <a href="https://ko-fi.com/s/cdcf15d085">a physical copy</a> from my online shop! It'll mean a lot to me. =) </p>
